column2: "Sukuna-hime..."
"It hast been a while, Kuron King. I arrived in response to thy missive. The contents of our talk shouldst be obvious?"
"Forgive me."
"What?"
"Sukuna-hime. Please, run."
"King!"
"No good, no good. Can't have a copy mouthing off on its own."
"We put in just a little humanity and pop. He's gone, gone."
"[Double]...!"
"You fiends... You consumed him, didn't thee?"
"That's wrong, wrong, wrong. Just him would be lonely, so we ate them all."
"Ha, you mad, you mad, you scary. But we know, you wasted a lot of power dealing with [Magatsu]?"
"No matter how much of a Miko you are, in your condition..."
"In your state, there's no way you can stand in our way."
"<%me>! Get Sukuna-hime!"
"Nn, thanks for the meal. That wasn't entirely as planned, but oh well, it was yummy."
"<%me>! Matoi! Whither art thee?! I can't sense thee anywhere...!"
"Fiends... even mine own friends, <%me> and Matoi!"
"Nn? Nnn? You called? Called? You called us?"
"I am her."
"I am him."
"My coming out from myself shouldn't be that strange."
"Not a strange thing about it. Me and I are [Double]."
"Miko, wanna go? Wanna fight with me?"
"Then I'll eat you. I want to eat you more and more..."
"What? What's wrong? Did you eat them properly?"
"Yup, ate them well. ...But, it feels different from usual."
"Kuron King"
